{
  "name": "Illuminate",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "icons/magic/light/orbs-firefly-hand-yellow.webp",
  "system": {
    "itemKey": "",
    "description": "<p>You attempt to illuminate every creature within a 3 Space diameter Sphere within range.</p><p>Make a Spell Check contested by the Repeated Charisma Save of each creature in the area.</p><p><strong>Save Failure:</strong> For the duration, the creature emits a 1 Space radius of Dim Light and can't benefit from being Concealed (such as being Invisible).</p><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Spell Enhancements</span></strong></span></p><p><strong>Range: (1 AP, Repeatable) </strong>The range of the Spell increases by 5 Spaces. You can use this Enhancement a maximum of two times.</p><p><strong>Area: (1 MP, Repeatable)</strong> The Sphere’s diameter is increased by 1 Space.</p><p><strong>Duration: (1 MP)</strong> The duration increases by 1 minute.</p><p><strong>Expose: (2 MP)</strong> On a failed Save, the target becomes Exposed for the duration.</p><p><strong>Blinded: (4 MP)</strong> On a failed Save, the target becomes Blinded for the duration.</p>",
